                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3293" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0207</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9576 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">竭智尽忠还是朝秦暮楚：编外员工的忠诚度悖论</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Be fully intellectual and loyal or be quickly switch sides: the paradox of supernumerary staff loyalty</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许广永，田雪莉，孙敏，刘晶晶</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蚌埠医院</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编外员工；忠诚度；离职；2018百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">supernumerary staff; loyalty; desert jobs</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着我国医疗事业的发展，医院仅靠编制内的员工已满足不了其快速发展的需求。医院患者数量增加与医护人员不足的矛盾日益加剧，医院编制受限，迫使医院通过大量招聘编外员工来弥补人员的不足。然而，由于许多医院对于编内员工和编外员工在薪酬福利及其他方面区别对待，使得编外员工对医院的忠诚度不高，进而导致编外员工大量离职，给人力资源管理工作带来新的难题，这很大程度对医院的持续良性发展产生了负面影响。因此，怎样革新现有管理制度以提高编外员工的忠诚度，降低编外员工的离职率是医院急需要解决的问题。本案例以安徽省地方三甲医院，蚌埠医院近几年编外员工离职率越来越高为背景，回顾了蚌埠医院近几年对医疗人才的大量需求，以及编外员工忠诚度越来越低、流失严重，重点描述了蚌埠医院编外人才忠诚度低的主要原因以及大量流失给医院带来的负面影响,展现了提高编外员工忠诚度对于降低员工流失以及医院发展的重要意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the development of China&#39;s medical industry, the hospital&#39;s employees in the preparation alone have not met their rapid development needs. The collision of increase patients and the medical personnel shortage have intensified, and the number of employees in hospitals is limited, forcing the hospital to make up for staff shortages by recruiting a large number of supernumeraries. However, because many hospitals discriminate between employees and non-staff members in terms of compensation and benefits, and other aspects, the supernumerary employees&#39; loyalty to the hospital is not high, which in turn leads to the massive turnover of non-supernumerary employees and brings new human resource management work. The problem, to a certain extent, has had a negative impact on the planning and development of the hospital. Therefore, how to renovate the existing management system to increase the loyalty of the non-staff employees and reduce the turnover of non-staff employees is one of the urgent problems for the hospital. This case is based on the fact that the local top three hospitals in Anhui Province and the hospitals have a higher turnover rate of non-standard employees in recent years. It reviewed the high demand for medical personnel in y hospitals in recent years and the low and extra staff loyalty of employees. The phenomenon of loss has focused on the main reasons for the low loyalty of the non-standard personnel in y hospitals and the negative impact on the hospital caused by the massive loss of talents, demonstrating the importance of increasing the loyalty of non-compliance employees and reducing staff turnover and hospital development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">员工忠诚度；员工离职与员工忠诚度；组织承诺；组织文化；心理契约；工作满意度；薪酬体系设计；招聘与培训；沟通；公平理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018-07</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
